name: BAISHUN
description:
baishun, is a combination of two kanji characters, the first meaning 'to sell' and the second meaning 'spring', as in season. So, to sell youth, innocence, promise of life to come.

this robot is a sex worker robot or prostitute, but this robot is also designed to kill, uncle jack is the one who designed this robot which he made to satisfy the sexual desires of rich people, but behind it all Uncle jack's real goal is to know the secrets of state officials and corruptors, even some of the robots have killed influential people in their country, state officials and corruptors
